---
layout: base.njk
title: "Prelims Practice"
description: "UPSC Prelims MCQ practice — topic-wise quizzes, timed mock tests, and PYQ-based practice sets for GS Paper 1."
---

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span class="breadcrumb__sep">/</span>
      Prelims Practice
    </nav>
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Test Yourself</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Prelims MCQ Practice</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">Topic-wise quizzes, timed mock tests, and PYQ-based practice sets. Track your accuracy across subjects.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding:var(--space-8) 0;">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Stats Dashboard -->
    <div id="prelims-stats" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-4); margin-bottom:var(--space-8);"></div>

    <!-- Quick Start -->
    <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-10);">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:var(--text-2xl); color:var(--color-brand-dark); margin-bottom:var(--space-5); padding-bottom:var(--space-2); border-bottom:3px solid var(--color-accent);">Quick Start</h2>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-5);">
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--color-accent);">
          <h3 class="card__title">10-Question Sprint</h3>
          <p class="card__desc">Random mix from all subjects. 10 minutes. Perfect for daily practice.</p>
          <button class="btn btn--accent btn--sm start-quiz" data-mode="sprint" style="margin-top:var(--space-3);">Start Sprint</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid var(--color-brand);">
          <h3 class="card__title">Full Mock (100 Qs)</h3>
          <p class="card__desc">Simulate real UPSC Prelims GS-1. 100 questions, 2 hours, negative marking.</p>
          <button class="btn btn--primary btn--sm start-quiz" data-mode="full" style="margin-top:var(--space-3);">Start Mock</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid #16a34a;">
          <h3 class="card__title">PYQ Practice</h3>
          <p class="card__desc">Actual UPSC questions from past years. The best way to understand the exam.</p>
          <button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm start-quiz" data-mode="pyq" style="margin-top:var(--space-3);">Start PYQs</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Topic-wise Practice -->
    <div style="margin-bottom:var(--space-10);">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:var(--text-2xl); color:var(--color-brand-dark); margin-bottom:var(--space-5); padding-bottom:var(--space-2); border-bottom:3px solid var(--color-accent);">Topic-wise Practice</h2>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-4);">

        {% set subjects = [
          { name: "Polity & Constitution", icon: "⚖️", slug: "polity", color: "#9d174d" },
          { name: "Indian Economy", icon: "💰", slug: "economy", color: "#065f46" },
          { name: "Environment & Ecology", icon: "🌿", slug: "environment", color: "#16a34a" },
          { name: "Science & Technology", icon: "🔬", slug: "science-tech", color: "#7c3aed" },
          { name: "History & Culture", icon: "🏛️", slug: "history-culture", color: "#1e40af" },
          { name: "Geography", icon: "🌍", slug: "geography", color: "#b45309" },
          { name: "International Relations", icon: "🤝", slug: "international-relations", color: "#0e7490" },
          { name: "Current Affairs", icon: "📰", slug: "current-affairs", color: "#dc2626" }
        ] %}

        {% for subj in subjects %}
        <div class="card topic-quiz-card" data-subject="{{ subj.slug }}">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:var(--space-2); margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">
            <span style="font-size:1.5rem;">{{ subj.icon }}</span>
            <h4 style="color:{{ subj.color }}; font-size:var(--text-base); font-weight:var(--font-bold);">{{ subj.name }}</h4>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:var(--space-3);">
            <span class="topic-score" style="font-size:var(--text-xs); color:var(--color-text-muted);">No attempts yet</span>
            <button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm start-quiz" data-mode="topic" data-subject="{{ subj.slug }}">Practice</button>
          </div>
          <!-- Accuracy bar -->
          <div style="background:var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-full); height:4px; margin-top:var(--space-2); overflow:hidden;">
            <div class="accuracy-bar" style="background:{{ subj.color }}; height:100%; width:0%; border-radius:var(--radius-full); transition:width 0.3s;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quiz Container (hidden until quiz starts) -->
    <div id="quiz-container" hidden>
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:var(--space-4); flex-wrap:wrap; gap:var(--space-3);">
        <div>
          <span id="quiz-mode-label" style="font-size:var(--text-sm); font-weight:var(--font-bold); color:var(--color-brand);"></span>
          <span id="quiz-progress" style="font-size:var(--text-sm); color:var(--color-text-muted); margin-left:var(--space-2);"></span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:var(--space-3);">
          <span id="quiz-timer" style="font-size:var(--text-sm); font-weight:var(--font-bold); color:var(--color-accent);"></span>
          <button id="quiz-quit" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm">End Quiz</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Timer bar -->
      <div style="background:var(--color-border); border-radius:var(--radius-full); height:4px; margin-bottom:var(--space-6); overflow:hidden;">
        <div id="timer-bar" style="background:var(--color-accent); height:100%; width:100%; border-radius:var(--radius-full); transition:width 1s linear;"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="max-width:720px; margin:0 auto;">
        <div id="quiz-question" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-5);">
          <p id="q-text" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:var(--text-lg); line-height:var(--leading-relaxed); color:var(--color-brand-dark); font-weight:var(--font-semibold); margin-bottom:var(--space-4);"></p>
          <div id="q-options"></div>
        </div>
        <div id="quiz-feedback" hidden style="padding:var(--space-4); border-radius:var(--radius-md); margin-bottom:var(--space-4);"></div>
        <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between;">
          <button id="q-prev" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" hidden>Previous</button>
          <button id="q-next" class="btn btn--accent btn--sm">Next</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Results (hidden until quiz ends) -->
    <div id="quiz-results" hidden>
      <div class="card" style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:var(--text-2xl); color:var(--color-brand-dark); margin-bottom:var(--space-4);">Quiz Complete!</h2>
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:var(--space-4); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">
          <div>
            <div id="result-score" style="font-size:var(--text-3xl); font-weight:var(--font-extrabold); color:var(--color-brand);"></div>
            <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm); color:var(--color-text-muted);">Score</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div id="result-accuracy" style="font-size:var(--text-3xl); font-weight:var(--font-extrabold); color:var(--color-accent);"></div>
            <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm); color:var(--color-text-muted);">Accuracy</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div id="result-time" style="font-size:var(--text-3xl); font-weight:var(--font-extrabold); color:var(--color-text-muted);"></div>
            <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm); color:var(--color-text-muted);">Time</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="result-review" style="text-align:left; margin-bottom:var(--space-6);"></div>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:var(--space-3); justify-content:center;">
          <button class="btn btn--accent" onclick="location.reload()">Try Again</button>
          <a href="/prelims/" class="btn btn--ghost">Back to Prelims</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How Prelims Scoring Works -->
    <div style="margin-top:var(--space-10);">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:var(--text-2xl); color:var(--color-brand-dark); margin-bottom:var(--space-5); padding-bottom:var(--space-2); border-bottom:3px solid var(--color-accent);">How UPSC Prelims Scoring Works</h2>
      <div class="card article-body" style="max-width:720px;">
        <h4>GS Paper 1 (General Studies)</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Total questions:</strong> 100</li>
          <li><strong>Maximum marks:</strong> 200 (2 marks per question)</li>
          <li><strong>Negative marking:</strong> -0.66 marks (1/3rd) for each wrong answer</li>
          <li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Qualifying:</strong> Must clear both GS and CSAT to qualify for Mains</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>CSAT Paper 2</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Total questions:</strong> 80</li>
          <li><strong>Maximum marks:</strong> 200 (2.5 marks per question)</li>
          <li><strong>Negative marking:</strong> -0.83 marks (1/3rd) for each wrong answer</li>
          <li><strong>Qualifying marks:</strong> 33% (66/200) — only qualifying, not counted for merit</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Strategy Tips</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Attempt only when you can eliminate at least 2 options — random guessing loses marks</li>
          <li>Aim for 90+ correct with under 15 wrong for a safe score</li>
          <li>Time management: ~1.2 minutes per question — flag and revisit tough ones</li>
          <li>Current affairs make up 30-40% of GS Paper 1 — stay updated via <a href="https://ujiyari.com/daily/" target="_blank">Ujiyari.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<script src="/js/prelims-quiz.js" defer></script>
